# U.S.S. Tiger

### a [MaxPower](http://maxpower.tk), [SebeL](http://sebel-industries.tk) and [KlickyNiko](http://klickyniko.tk) project

### U.S.S. Tiger is a text based adventure game, that belongs to the Star Trek Universe.

> ## It is currently in pre-alpha state!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
